8 <a href="javascript:card_browser(238)">Shores of Nen Hithoel</a> <br>
9 <a href="javascript:card_browser(242)">Summit of Amon Hen</a> <br>
<br>
Free Peoples (31 excluding Starting) <br>
Gandalf, FotSF x3 <br>
